                            p.lead The Apollo Protocol: unifying digital twins across sectors, the paper that launched the initiative
                    .col-lg-4
                        .features-icons-item.mx-auto.mb-5.mb-lg-0.mb-lg-3
                            .features-icons-icon.d-flex
                                i.bi-diagram-3.m-auto.text-primary
                            h3 DTHub
                            p.lead Join the growing network on the Digital Twin Hub
                    .col-lg-4
                        .features-icons-item.mx-auto.mb-0.mb-lg-3
                            .features-icons-icon.d-flex
                                i.bi-wrench.m-auto.text-primary
                            h3 Activity Modeller
                            p.lead Learn and practice planning in a new way. Helping you discover all the information you need for complete decision making and resource planning.
                .row
                    .col-lg-4
                        a.btn.btn-primary(href='https://www.theiet.org/impact-society/factfiles/built-environment-factfiles/the-apollo-protocol-unifying-digital-twins-across-sectors/') Download
                    .col-lg-4
                        a.btn.btn-primary(href='#!') Join
                    .col-lg-4
                        a.btn.btn-primary(href='https://apollo-protocol.github.io/4d-activity-editor/') Visit

